title: Full House - 2x07 - Joey Gets Tough
description:
29. Joey Gets Tough
First aired: 11/25/1988
Writer: Lenny Ripps 
Director: Peter Baldwin 
Guest star: Lori Loughlin, (Rebecca Donaldson), Richard Paul(Mr. Strowbridge), Laurie Carr (Miss Kadota Fig)


Joey let&#039;s DJ and Stephanie watch a Tiffany concert. Danny comes in and Joey decides to be tougher. DJ comes home late and he won&#039;t let her go to her karate tournament.
